name: Imagine This
description:
Imagine This...

You have managed to escape the hustle and the bustle of the grind we call life. You're with your partner, strolling along the beach enjoying the peace and quiet of a dead flat high tide.

The darkness is starting to settle just as the full moon times it perfectly and you discover what is simply the most beautiful little rock pool on a warmish kind of night.

You can't pass up this view! Its time for a coldie in the rock pool and perhaps a bit of cuddle time...
